description:
Check out the trailer for the upcoming Sagat Arrives! Fighting Pass for Street Fighter 6. The Sagat Arrives! Fighting Pass includes a new outfit for Ryu and Ken, emotes, avatar gear, and more! Don't miss the Sagat Arrives! Fighting Pass when Sagat arrives as the latest playable Street Fighter 6 character on August 5, 2025. 

Street Fighter 6 is available now on PlayStation 5 (PS5), PlayStation 4 (PS4), Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch 2 and PC.

title: Street Fighter 6 - Official Sagat Arrives! Fighting Pass Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Check out the 'Lift Off' Teaser Trailer for The Fantastic Four: First Steps, the next installment and the introduction of Marvel's First Family to the MCU, distributed by Marvel Studios. Get a look at more shots, including an intense chase scene through the cosmos with The Fantastic Four and the Silver Surfer. The Fantastic Four: First Steps is relasing in theaters on July 25.

The Fantastic Four: First Steps stars Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Joseph Quinn, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, Ralph Ineson, and Julia Garner. The Fantastic Four: First Steps opens in theaters on July 25, 2025.

Set against the vibrant backdrop of a 1960s-inspired, retro- futuristic world, Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps introduces Marvel’s First Family—Reed Richards/Mister Fantastic (Pedro Pascal), Sue Storm/Invisible Woman (Vanessa Kirby), Johnny Storm/Human Torch (Joseph Quinn) and Ben Grimm/The Thing (Ebon Moss-Bachrach) as they face their most daunting challenge yet. Forced to balance their roles as
title: The Fantastic Four: First Steps - Official 'Lift Off' Teaser (2025) Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby

author: IGN
description:
We got Dr Kenneth Lacovara, an American palaeontologist and geologist at Rowan University, known for discovering the Dreadnoughtus dinosaur, to react to, breakdown, and explain various dinosaurs shown throughout the Jurassic Park and Jurassic World series of films. So, are Velociraptors actually dangerous? Could a T-Rex really roar? Those, and more, answered!

#IGN #JurassicPark #JurassicWorld #JurassicWorldRebirth
title: How Realistic Are Dinosaurs in Jurassic World? Dinosaur Expert Explains

author: IGN
description:
In this snippet from Nintendo Voice Chat Ep 768, Our final Donkey Kong Bananza preview is here, and we’re totally in love with what we’ve played of the upcoming 3D platformer. This week, join Logan Plant, Seth Macy, Reb Valentine, and Mitchell Saltzman as they dive into Mitchell’s Bananza preview, including thoughts on DK’s moveset, the challenge rooms, the Bananza transformations, and the confirmation that the team behind Super Mario Odyssey is working on Bananza. 

This weeks show is Logan Plant, Seth Macy, Rebekah Valentine, Mitchell Saltzman, and is produced by Nick Maillet.

#IGN #Gaming #Nintendo
title: We Played DK Bananza, and it's Bigger, Faster, and Stronger, Too - NVC Clips
